@NODE Voraus " What need MEWandel"

	MEWandel needs OS2.0 and a AMIGA, not more.
	MEWandel is tested only on a AMIGA 500 (OS3.0, 68020,
	9 MB RAM, 520 MB AT-HD).

@ENDNODE
	
@NODE Kann " What do MEWandel?"

	MEWandel is an Commodity, which change Numbers with Base
	2-62 and roman-Numbers in each another.

	MEWandel use the standart-tooltypes for Commodities
	(CX_POPKEY,CX_POPUP,CX_PRIORITY).

@ENDNODE

@NODE install " Installation"

	Use the installer-script...

@ENDNODE

@NODE bedienung " Usage"

	I thing its easy.... You can change the numbers in @{"MainWindow" LINK "Haupt"}.
	In the @{"Prefswindow" LINK "Prefs"} you can edit the Tooltypes.
	
@ENDNODE

@NODE Haupt " Mainwindow"

	If you change from/to Roman you must set from/to at one,
	or write a "r" in the String-Gadget of the end of the 
	sliders. In this Gadget you can enter also:
	- B,b,% : for bin 	  (Base  2)
	- O,o   : for octal	  (Base  8)
	- D,d 	: for decimal 	  (Base 10)
	- H,h,$ : for hexadecimal (Base 16)

	MEWandel use at bases, up to
	- 10 the digits 0-9
	- 36 the gigits 0-9 and A-Z
	- 62 the digits 0-9, A-Z and a-z
		
@ENDNODE

@NODE Prefs "Prefswindow"

	Here you can edit the typical commodity tooltypes.

@ENDNODE

@NODE ARexx "ARexx-Port"
	
	The ARexx-Port knows this commands:
	
	- Quit:
		quit the programm
	- Show:
		show the main window
	- Hide:
		hide the main window
	- Help:
		shows a help text
	- Wandel:
		with this command you can convert a number,
		th Syntax is:
		From:To:Number

	A sample ARexx-Script is included.

@ENDNODE

@NODE version " Versions"

	@{b}Version 1.0 (15.03.1998)@{ub}
	- change Dezimal/Hex/Bin/Octal/Roman numbers into each other

	@{b}Version 1.01 (31.03.1998)@{ub}
	- Remove the mistake in x to roman-numbers
	
	@{b}Version 2.0 (22.11.1998)@{ub}
	- Complete rewriten
	- Tooltype can chnage in the program
	- You can now change Bases 2-62

	@{b}Version 2.2 (09.01.1999)@{ub}
	- Menus are now in the New-Look layout
	- The Cancel-gadget in the prefswindow works now
	- The GUI is changed

	@{b}Version 2.3 (15.02.1999):@{ub}
	- Better installer-script
	- Improved guide
	- A simple Onlinehelp build in

	@{b}Version 2.4 (19.06.1999):@{ub}
	- Some Enforcer-Hits are removed
	- The onlinehelp is now asynchron
	- Some bugs removed
	- MEWandel works now with negativ numbers (exception: bin)
	- ARexx-Port

	@{b}Future:
	- Better handling of negativ numbers
	
@ENDNODE

